  "title": "Part-Time English Camp Helper (Singapore)",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a Part-Time English Camp Helper to join\nour team in Singapore. The staff member is hired as a part-time staff\nmember for the camp period ; Apr, Jul, and Oct 2026. This is a temporary position, and employment ends upon camp completion.</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Supervise and support campers</li><li>Assist in English sessions and activities</li><li>Help with meals, games, and excursions</li><li>Ensure camper safety</li><li>Speak English during camp time</li><li>Participate actively and with motivation</li><li>Be punctual and follow the camp schedule</li><li>Follow staff rules and instructions</li><li>Provide reports as requested and required by Berlitz</li><li>Abide by all local laws and regulations of the destination country</li></ul><p><strong>Working Hours</strong></p><ul><li>Working hours are from 13:30 to 18:30</li><li>5 days during the camp period</li></ul><p><em>The schedule includes weekends and public holiday.</em></p><p><strong>Code of Conduct</strong></p><ul><li>Be professional and respectful at all times</li><li>No smoking, alcohol, or inappropriate behavior</li><li>Phones may be used for taking photos or videos of students for camp purposes only</li><li>Keep camp information and activities confidential. Do not share with competitors or related camps.</li><li>Do not post photos or content online without permission</li><li>Maintain a safe, friendly, and encouraging environment</li><li>Keep all camper and staff information confidential</li></ul><p><strong>Visa / Work Permit Requirements</strong></p><p>-Singapore citizens and PR holders</p><p>-LTVP+ and DP holders may apply but will be assessed on a\ncase-by-case basis</p>",
