    "description": "<p>Berlitz is a market leader in language instruction, cross-cultural consulting and global leadership training throughout the world. As the largest language training services provider in the world, Berlitz has been teaching languages for over 140 years, and offers training in over 50+ languages, and has helped over 31 million people speak new languages. The time-proven principles of the Berlitz Method, a communicative teaching approach, are constantly enhanced with new and updated programs and the latest learning technology.</p>\n",
